textRun.content: Document Import — Bulk Entry Stress Test
Overview

This document is designed to test the importer's ability to handle large-scale document parsing, specifically to validate rate-limit management and pagination logic. It contains over 100 heading-and-paragraph pairs to simulate heavy import workloads.
